reviewText: This is a must see for all the emasculated men in America who have lost touch with their "inner man". I loved this sexy primer for getting men out of their mundane worlds into the life they were meant to have with plenty of sexy play between the sexes. Yeah, the feminists want to shut down any good times men want to have with the ladies but in this film a mysterious woman comes into the last private men's club in town to show them how to reclaim their manhood and get laid along the way. It's jam-packed with sexy good times with lots of naked women along the way, what else could a man ask for? It's all here... it's all here..
